Key Match Events: Haris Rauf and Hasan Ali led Pakistan's pace attack to stop Netherlands at the score 205
Bas de Leede scored the highest 67 runs while Vikramjit Singh smashed 52 runs for Netherlands
Hasan Ali dismissed Max O'Dowd and Colin Ackermann
Bas de Leede took 4 wickets for 62 runs
Mohammad Rizwan and Saud Shakeel played in a wonderful partnership to pull back Pakistan from a low-scoring end
